text: Joaquín Hermida (born 16 August 1921) was a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
